<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Advanced Placement (AP) credit will be determined provided the official examination score reports are forwarded directly to Merrimack College (code: 3525).

As a participant in the Advanced Placement Program of the College Board, Merrimack College will grant both credit and advanced placement to students who present examination scores of at least 3 on Advanced Placement tests offered by the Educational Testing Service.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.merrimack.edu/admissions/undergraduate/getintouch/faqs.php" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
